WEBVTT

01:37.850 --> 01:40.390
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.460 --> 01:43.640
[Episode 15]

01:44.640 --> 01:45.970
Back then, the War Demon

01:46.039 --> 01:47.370
planted the sacred seed

01:48.039 --> 01:50.070
of the divine tree
to repair the heavenly ladder,

01:50.070 --> 01:53.070
vainly attempting to sacrifice
half the mortal population

01:53.070 --> 01:54.200
to awaken it.

01:54.970 --> 01:56.450
Once the people found out,

01:56.479 --> 01:57.920
they rose up in rebellion,

01:57.920 --> 01:59.509
sparking countless wars

01:59.840 --> 02:01.570
with millions dead or injured.

02:02.040 --> 02:02.760
Even so,

02:03.380 --> 02:05.180
many villages and ancient towns

02:05.310 --> 02:06.710
still managed to endure.

02:07.070 --> 02:08.110
But it's strange.

02:08.520 --> 02:10.400
The world has been peaceful
in recent years,

02:10.400 --> 02:12.260
yet things are worse than before.

02:15.030 --> 02:16.890
Is it only when a great war strikes

02:17.079 --> 02:19.430
and the Human Race
faces the danger of extinction

02:19.430 --> 02:21.430
that the immortal sects will remember

02:21.430 --> 02:22.630
that we and the people

02:23.280 --> 02:24.540
are of the same origin?

02:28.590 --> 02:30.710
What I originally wanted
to ask you is,

02:30.710 --> 02:31.970
if you were a commoner,

02:32.430 --> 02:34.290
would you stay home and pay taxes,

02:34.520 --> 02:36.780
or abandon your land to become a refugee?

02:44.590 --> 02:45.560
It seems

02:46.240 --> 02:47.120
that you

02:47.120 --> 02:48.520
cannot give me an answer.

03:11.870 --> 03:13.910
The question you just asked

03:15.240 --> 03:16.900
was meant to put us on the spot?

03:21.680 --> 03:22.880
Senior Uncle Gong Yu,

03:23.030 --> 03:24.160
why did you say that?

03:25.150 --> 03:27.000
We dedicate ourselves to cultivation

03:27.000 --> 03:28.260
with no distractions,

03:28.310 --> 03:29.400
and we have lived
in the mountains for a long time,

03:29.400 --> 03:30.870
keeping ourselves removed
from worldly affairs.

03:30.870 --> 03:33.240
Today is the first time I've heard of

03:33.680 --> 03:36.120
the Immortality Tax you mentioned.

03:37.030 --> 03:39.290
You also said your Dao heart is unstable,

03:39.360 --> 03:41.220
and your realm has fallen 3 times.

03:41.630 --> 03:42.829
This is enough to show

03:43.190 --> 03:45.720
that you have
too many distracting thoughts.

03:45.800 --> 03:46.560
Yet you

03:46.750 --> 03:48.030
not only never restrain them,

03:48.030 --> 03:49.560
but even allow them to grow!

03:50.680 --> 03:51.680
I am slow-witted.

03:52.280 --> 03:53.960
Please enlighten me, Senior Uncle.

03:53.960 --> 03:56.820
How can I rid myself
of these distracting thoughts?

03:57.310 --> 03:58.240
Do you know

03:58.360 --> 04:00.590
the origin of the Sun Moon Cavern?

04:01.630 --> 04:02.630
I heard that the Sun Moon Cavern

04:02.630 --> 04:04.310
practices the Way of Great Unity,

04:04.310 --> 04:05.710
emphasizing non-contention
and non-seeking,

04:05.710 --> 04:07.170
no desire and no delusion,

04:07.400 --> 04:08.630
unity of heaven and man,

04:08.630 --> 04:09.860
and the great unity of all things.

04:09.860 --> 04:11.590
It shares similar merits
with Tianyin Mountain's

04:11.590 --> 04:12.560
forgetting of both self and world,

04:12.560 --> 04:14.690
and the impartiality of the Great Way.

04:15.430 --> 04:17.160
No, no.

04:18.070 --> 04:20.750
Our sect advocates
that the world is for all

04:21.510 --> 04:24.430
and that all things are treated
as the true foundation.

04:24.430 --> 04:25.760
If all beings are equal,

04:26.000 --> 04:28.430
how then do we distinguish
magnitude or importance?

04:28.430 --> 04:29.800
The infinitely great has no exterior.

04:29.800 --> 04:31.000
The infinitely small has no interior.

04:31.000 --> 04:33.260
One is the infinite; The infinite is one.

04:33.750 --> 04:35.280
The two words you mentioned

04:35.510 --> 04:36.680
are inherently one.

04:37.000 --> 04:38.800
Is there no distinction of size,

04:38.800 --> 04:40.560
no sense of priority or urgency?

04:40.560 --> 04:41.680
Are humans no different

04:41.680 --> 04:42.630
from birds, beasts,

04:42.630 --> 04:44.230
flowers, fish, and insects?

04:44.230 --> 04:45.830
All living beings are equal.

04:46.450 --> 04:48.360
All things are the same.

04:48.930 --> 04:49.840
Then, once you

04:49.870 --> 04:51.310
exchange the five Gongshan Jade Tablets

04:51.310 --> 04:52.680
for the Immortal Pills,

04:52.870 --> 04:54.360
how will they be distributed?

04:54.360 --> 04:56.040
Since all living beings are equal,

04:56.040 --> 04:56.630
Senior Uncle,

04:56.630 --> 04:59.510
are you willing to distribute them
to the disciples behind you?

04:59.510 --> 05:00.240
How about it?

05:03.500 --> 05:04.700
All beings are equal,

05:04.950 --> 05:06.120
yet humans are divided into
high and low, noble and base,

05:06.120 --> 05:07.580
and many different ranks.

05:07.870 --> 05:08.830
Is this the Way of Great Unity

05:08.830 --> 05:09.560
you pursue?

05:09.720 --> 05:10.160
Xin...

05:12.830 --> 05:14.030
Extremely arrogant!

05:14.310 --> 05:15.910
You are extremely arrogant!

05:21.040 --> 05:22.070
When disciples enter the immortal sect,

05:22.070 --> 05:23.560
they must swear by their Dao heart.

05:23.560 --> 05:24.350
The first vow

05:24.560 --> 05:25.680
is not to use immortal arts

05:25.680 --> 05:27.270
to interfere in mortal affairs.

05:27.270 --> 05:28.270
Then I want to ask,

05:28.600 --> 05:30.680
does the existence of the Immortality Pill
and Immortality Tax

05:30.680 --> 05:33.540
count as immortals interfering
in mortal affairs?

05:38.270 --> 05:39.630
I am not a cultivator.

05:40.040 --> 05:42.870
I don't know enough
about the immortal sect's vows.

05:42.870 --> 05:43.680
Moreover,

05:44.440 --> 05:45.400
I also often have

05:45.430 --> 05:46.630
similar confusions.

05:47.480 --> 05:49.190
I have been an official
in the court for 10 years.

05:49.190 --> 05:50.520
Because of my position,

05:50.720 --> 05:51.920
I am considered one of the Human Race

05:51.920 --> 05:53.870
who has more contact
with the immortal sect.

05:53.870 --> 05:55.330
I have seen with my own eyes

05:55.360 --> 05:57.510
that some cultivators hold fast
to their Dao heart

05:57.510 --> 05:58.770
and behave uprightly,

05:59.040 --> 06:01.230
yet merely using a bit of immortal magic

06:01.230 --> 06:02.430
causes their cultivation
to be greatly damaged

06:02.430 --> 06:03.760
and their realm to fall.

06:04.210 --> 06:05.360
Meanwhile, some cultivators

06:05.360 --> 06:06.770
act recklessly in the mortal world,

06:06.770 --> 06:08.270
killing and committing sins,

06:08.270 --> 06:10.730
yet their Dao heart is not seen
to be damaged.

06:11.650 --> 06:12.680
So, as for your question, Miss,

06:12.680 --> 06:14.510
if I must give an answer,

06:14.510 --> 06:15.750
I can only guess

06:16.160 --> 06:17.070
that these vows

06:17.510 --> 06:19.270
are not rigid like the laws
of the mortal world,

06:19.270 --> 06:20.800
constrained by others.

06:21.360 --> 06:22.360
It is more like...

06:23.120 --> 06:23.750
belief.

06:24.190 --> 06:25.950
It all depends on self-discipline.

06:25.950 --> 06:28.070
If one's own belief is shallow,

06:28.610 --> 06:31.070
it cannot serve
as a true guiding principle.

06:32.070 --> 06:33.470
You are a human official.

06:33.750 --> 06:35.280
Then what is your position?

06:36.159 --> 06:37.360
I'm Zhi Bocheng,

06:38.070 --> 06:40.220
Jingzhou Transport
and Communications Envoy.

06:40.220 --> 06:42.120
You said you have been
an official for ten years.

06:42.120 --> 06:44.180
You must have seen all aspects of life

06:44.360 --> 06:46.090
and the suffering of the world.

06:46.120 --> 06:47.390
But you still traveled thousands of miles

06:47.390 --> 06:49.720
across mountains and rivers to come here.

06:50.000 --> 06:51.800
From what standpoint do you act,

06:51.800 --> 06:53.070
and who are you getting the elixir for?

06:53.070 --> 06:55.190
I receive the king's salary
and share his worries.

06:55.190 --> 06:56.600
I am His Majesty's subject

06:56.600 --> 06:57.830
and an envoy of the court.

06:57.830 --> 06:59.630
I have my own duties.

07:00.160 --> 07:01.430
This is my stance.

07:03.270 --> 07:05.330
Not for the many, but for a single man.

07:05.870 --> 07:07.800
So it's not just the immortal sect.

07:07.800 --> 07:09.200
You are all no different.

07:10.120 --> 07:12.050
You've answered all my questions.

07:12.360 --> 07:14.220
These two jade tablets are yours.

07:15.430 --> 07:16.630
Thank you, Miss.

07:19.870 --> 07:20.920
But His Majesty

07:21.680 --> 07:24.340
only asked me
to bring back 6 Immortality Pills.

07:25.510 --> 07:26.640
I already have them.

07:35.600 --> 07:37.130
Thank you, Miss Xin,

07:38.750 --> 07:40.480
for speaking up for the people.

08:04.070 --> 08:04.930
Junior Sister.

08:08.310 --> 08:09.970
I have asked all my questions.

08:10.510 --> 08:11.910
I have no more questions.

08:16.560 --> 08:17.360
Senior Uncle.

08:24.310 --> 08:24.920
Senior.

08:26.800 --> 08:27.310
Senior.

08:27.720 --> 08:29.170
The Immortality Pill is about to
be completed.

08:29.170 --> 08:30.070
I hope you

08:30.170 --> 08:31.950
can give Chongling Valley some face.

08:31.950 --> 08:33.409
Do not stir up trouble here

08:33.600 --> 08:35.320
and affect my master's mood.

08:40.000 --> 08:41.460
Don't let me see you again.

09:18.870 --> 09:22.150
[Healing the World]

09:40.150 --> 09:41.010
Senior Sister.

09:41.390 --> 09:42.000
Sheng.

09:45.510 --> 09:46.370
Senior Sister.

10:03.870 --> 10:04.870
I was late.

10:07.080 --> 10:08.140
How did you find me?

10:08.630 --> 10:10.560
The mockingbird tracked you down.

10:11.270 --> 10:12.130
Senior Sister.

10:12.550 --> 10:13.810
Were you wronged here?

10:14.390 --> 10:15.190
How could I be?

10:15.750 --> 10:16.550
You don't know

10:16.720 --> 10:18.630
how good I felt speaking my mind today.

10:18.630 --> 10:20.360
They were all left speechless.

10:20.630 --> 10:21.240
Here,

10:22.000 --> 10:23.320
no one will wrong me.

10:23.920 --> 10:24.650
That's good.

10:25.910 --> 10:26.600
But you,

10:27.150 --> 10:28.550
you just ran out like this.

10:28.550 --> 10:29.880
Master must be furious.

10:30.320 --> 10:31.520
I'm not afraid of him.

10:38.600 --> 10:41.200
The Immortality Pill is about to
be completed.

11:36.870 --> 11:37.870
Divine Doctor Su.

11:38.080 --> 11:39.290
Long time no see.

11:46.450 --> 11:46.970
Well,

11:47.030 --> 11:48.360
you may step down first.

12:03.370 --> 12:04.000
Get out.

12:07.320 --> 12:08.120
My master said

12:08.270 --> 12:10.070
he doesn't want to see you later.

12:30.270 --> 12:31.930
Didn't you decide not to come?

12:32.750 --> 12:34.240
I want to see it with my own eyes.

12:34.240 --> 12:35.500
You are not the only one

12:35.790 --> 12:37.390
who understands those truths

12:37.390 --> 12:39.150
or the only one who is clear-headed.

12:39.150 --> 12:40.750
I'm not truly clear-headed.

12:40.870 --> 12:43.000
I just started to understand a little.

12:44.080 --> 12:44.600
Go back.

12:45.240 --> 12:47.240
All the immortal sects
have been waiting for decades.

12:47.240 --> 12:48.960
It's not just about immortality.

12:48.960 --> 12:51.220
It may well be the only way
forward for the immortal sects.

12:51.220 --> 12:52.030
Senior Sister,

12:52.030 --> 12:53.630
don't not waste words on him.

13:10.870 --> 13:12.030
Young Sect Master Lin.

13:12.030 --> 13:13.230
You haven't left yet?

13:13.320 --> 13:14.030
Whether I leave or not,

13:14.030 --> 13:15.760
what does it have to do with you?

13:15.910 --> 13:17.910
You don't even have
a Gongshan Jade Tablet.

13:17.910 --> 13:19.150
What are you doing here?

13:19.150 --> 13:19.960
Mr. Bai Yun.

13:20.640 --> 13:22.320
I'm not in a good mood today.

13:22.600 --> 13:23.670
Before you

13:24.120 --> 13:25.050
with your speak.

13:30.870 --> 13:32.130
Where is Bai Zongying?

13:32.200 --> 13:32.840
Those few

13:33.200 --> 13:34.200
are also not here.

13:42.320 --> 13:42.870
Do you still believe

13:42.870 --> 13:44.440
the Crazy Taoist's prophecy?

13:44.440 --> 13:45.270
He said that among
the Heavenly Talents born

13:45.270 --> 13:46.670
on September 9th,

13:47.030 --> 13:48.640
there will be the savior of the world.

13:48.640 --> 13:49.670
I really used to believe

13:49.670 --> 13:51.070
that person would be you.

13:51.870 --> 13:52.790
Is this how you prepare

13:52.790 --> 13:54.390
to be the savior of the world?

14:27.080 --> 14:27.950
Stoke the fire.

14:28.720 --> 14:29.200
Yes.

15:34.200 --> 15:35.000
Grandmaster.

15:35.000 --> 15:35.800
You're awake.

15:37.790 --> 15:39.320
These are not animal bones.

15:39.510 --> 15:41.640
Whose bones were these replaced with?

15:41.750 --> 15:42.550
Grandmaster,

15:43.230 --> 15:44.960
things have come to this point.

15:46.270 --> 15:47.270
Where is Su Taiyi?

16:10.440 --> 16:10.900
This...

16:11.670 --> 16:12.600
What is going on?

16:13.010 --> 16:14.200
They've started the alchemy.

16:14.200 --> 16:15.730
Why are they beating drums?

16:16.840 --> 16:18.510
Healers worship Shennong.

16:19.040 --> 16:20.550
Legend has it that in his early years,

16:20.550 --> 16:21.750
to taste hundreds of herbs,

16:21.750 --> 16:23.550
Shennong traveled through the forests.

16:23.550 --> 16:25.240
He carried a hand drum with him

16:25.510 --> 16:26.970
to scare away wild beasts.

16:27.550 --> 16:28.550
Later, to commemorate him,

16:28.550 --> 16:29.680
healers in the world

16:29.870 --> 16:31.960
composed music with drumbeats.

16:33.080 --> 16:34.480
There are melodies for thanking gods,

16:34.480 --> 16:35.790
sacrificial melodies,

16:35.790 --> 16:36.920
send-off melodies,

16:37.030 --> 16:39.360
victory melodies, and parting melodies.

16:39.520 --> 16:40.670
Today, these 28 drums

16:40.670 --> 16:41.670
playing together

16:42.240 --> 16:43.770
signify that this
furnace-opening ceremony

16:43.770 --> 16:45.500
is of unprecedented grandeur.

16:51.000 --> 16:52.000
That's not right.

16:53.270 --> 16:54.270
What's not right?

16:54.270 --> 16:56.150
This is clearly a joyous occasion.

16:56.150 --> 16:57.680
Why use the tune of parting?

16:59.680 --> 17:05.020
♪ A joyous meeting is hard to find again ♪

17:05.910 --> 17:11.579
♪ Three years feel like
a thousand autumns ♪

17:12.720 --> 17:18.720
♪ Washing my long tassels by the river ♪

17:19.069 --> 17:24.680
♪ My thoughts of you
are deep and mournful ♪

17:36.420 --> 17:38.440
Master and the others are at Jiujue Cave.

17:38.440 --> 17:39.750
The Immortality Elixir is produced today.

17:39.750 --> 17:41.610
Master has something to tell you.

17:42.720 --> 17:45.680
From a low-born entertainer

17:46.750 --> 17:48.920
who pleased others with songs

17:49.590 --> 17:50.510
to

17:51.270 --> 17:53.920
a world-renowned Divine Doctor,

17:55.030 --> 17:59.030
it is all because I was fortunate enough
to meet him.

18:00.790 --> 18:03.070
So I thought

18:03.880 --> 18:06.160
I must cherish this

18:06.960 --> 18:09.000
hard-won opportunity.

18:10.510 --> 18:13.110
Since I inherited these medical skills,

18:16.110 --> 18:18.240
I must achieve something great.

18:19.350 --> 18:21.240
I thought about it over and over.

18:22.000 --> 18:23.110
In this world,

18:24.000 --> 18:25.310
what else

18:27.750 --> 18:30.790
could be greater
than granting immortality?

18:32.150 --> 18:35.510
So I disobeyed him

18:37.070 --> 18:39.160
and built this Chongling Valley.

18:40.110 --> 18:42.030
I stubbornly went my own way

18:44.200 --> 18:45.830
until today.

18:47.680 --> 18:50.010
Although the Immortality Pills are good,

18:50.740 --> 18:53.220
they came at the wrong time

18:54.130 --> 18:56.040
and became a disaster instead.

18:59.510 --> 19:00.960
Look

19:02.950 --> 19:05.150
at the kind of people

19:05.170 --> 19:08.030
who come to Chongling Valley
to exchange medicine.

19:08.240 --> 19:10.270
What good would it do the world

19:11.550 --> 19:12.830
to give them

19:13.220 --> 19:15.350
the Immortal Pills?

19:16.920 --> 19:18.960
It is time to wake up

19:21.400 --> 19:24.050
from this dream of immortality.

19:26.640 --> 19:27.310
Master.

19:28.160 --> 19:29.690
Your intentions were good.

19:30.070 --> 19:31.930
You shouldn't be blamed for this.

19:32.110 --> 19:34.240
Grandmaster is also in the valley now.

19:34.680 --> 19:36.160
We can tell him

19:36.160 --> 19:37.160
about this matter.

19:37.160 --> 19:38.820
He will definitely have a way.

19:41.630 --> 19:43.820
I'm not young anymore.

19:45.000 --> 19:46.890
I can't keep causing trouble

19:49.420 --> 19:50.620
and leave everything

19:52.140 --> 19:54.620
for Master to clean up.

19:55.750 --> 19:57.070
My whole life

19:57.350 --> 19:58.790
has been full of sin,

19:59.240 --> 20:01.040
and my hands are soaked in blood.

20:01.440 --> 20:03.480
I've lived in confusion all my life,

20:04.350 --> 20:07.030
but at least my backbone is still firm.

20:07.720 --> 20:09.240
Even in front of the Emperor,

20:09.240 --> 20:12.270
I always kept my head high.

20:12.880 --> 20:15.070
If I give these bones to Master,

20:15.750 --> 20:17.350
he won't be at a loss.

20:18.880 --> 20:24.440
♪ Gazing afar, a mournful wind arrives ♪

20:24.680 --> 20:29.640
♪ Facing the wine,
I cannot raise a toast ♪

21:02.350 --> 21:08.070
♪ A joyous meeting is hard to find again ♪

21:08.830 --> 21:14.510
♪ Three years feel like
a thousand autumns ♪

21:15.440 --> 21:19.920
♪ Washing my long tassels by the river ♪

21:19.920 --> 21:21.240
Fine lyrics,

21:21.880 --> 21:23.030
fine melody,

21:23.960 --> 21:25.240
and a fine song!

21:27.160 --> 21:28.240
Good!

21:28.240 --> 21:33.590
♪ Gazing afar, a mournful wind arrives ♪

21:34.070 --> 21:39.310
♪ Facing the wine,
I cannot raise a toast ♪

21:40.640 --> 21:41.200
Master!

21:42.750 --> 21:43.270
Master.

21:44.000 --> 21:45.000
Divine Doctor Su.

21:47.790 --> 21:48.510
Master.

21:49.310 --> 21:50.030
Master!

21:54.160 --> 21:55.110
Master.

22:24.720 --> 22:26.750
Please tell him

22:28.310 --> 22:30.510
to grant me this wish.

22:31.160 --> 22:32.920
Take my bones

22:33.360 --> 22:34.930
and walk the path

22:34.960 --> 22:36.620
of the mortal world once more.

22:56.000 --> 22:56.960
It exploded.

24:00.000 --> 24:01.680
Before Master passed away,

24:02.230 --> 24:03.030
he instructed

24:04.350 --> 24:06.610
that these are all for you, Grandmaster.

24:06.880 --> 24:08.160
The items in this box

24:08.840 --> 24:10.500
are all emergency medicines.

24:10.640 --> 24:11.970
There are painkillers,

24:12.160 --> 24:13.640
medicine for stopping bleeding,

24:13.640 --> 24:15.570
and tonics to strengthen the body.

24:15.920 --> 24:17.160
He asked you

24:17.920 --> 24:19.320
to use them as you see fit.

24:23.830 --> 24:24.830
And this...

24:26.200 --> 24:27.000
Master

24:27.960 --> 24:29.880
bought you some property.

24:31.170 --> 24:31.890
He said

24:33.030 --> 24:35.310
you can have a place to stay

24:36.560 --> 24:38.160
wherever you go.

24:39.830 --> 24:40.640
Look.

24:42.000 --> 24:43.510
There's one in the capital,

24:43.510 --> 24:44.680
one in Wei County,

24:45.110 --> 24:46.880
one in Nanyang,

24:47.510 --> 24:49.310
and one in Jiuzhou.

24:52.270 --> 24:52.830
I have

24:53.110 --> 24:54.510
marked all the locations

24:58.820 --> 25:00.000
and left a butler there.

25:00.000 --> 25:00.850
When you go,

25:00.880 --> 25:02.010
just give your name.

25:08.200 --> 25:08.830
This one

25:09.590 --> 25:10.990
is even more impressive.

25:12.720 --> 25:13.920
These are the delicacies

25:13.920 --> 25:15.880
I've noted down from across the country

25:15.880 --> 25:17.400
over the years.

25:18.320 --> 25:19.680
I thought that now that
you have a sense of taste

25:19.680 --> 25:21.030
after the blood renewal,

25:21.030 --> 25:22.430
you could go and try them.

25:23.530 --> 25:25.400
The Six-Shrimp Noodles of Longshang,

25:25.400 --> 25:26.510
Kunlun Braised Abalone,

25:26.510 --> 25:27.510
Glazed Fish Bone,

25:27.680 --> 25:29.400
the Scholar Noodles from Jiangnan,

25:29.400 --> 25:30.680
Crab Roe Tofu,

25:31.000 --> 25:32.110
Xingdou Dian Yue,

25:32.200 --> 25:33.400
Yangtian Sandie,

25:33.750 --> 25:36.240
and Jiuzhen Jiucang from Dantu Town—

25:37.590 --> 25:40.650
all of them are supreme delicacies
of the mortal world.

25:41.750 --> 25:42.440
Moreover,

25:43.070 --> 25:44.680
we have properties

25:45.030 --> 25:46.160
in all these places.

25:46.790 --> 25:48.160
How carefree.

25:57.000 --> 25:57.860
There is no need

25:59.510 --> 26:00.970
to say more about this one.

26:01.400 --> 26:03.400
A War Demon can live without money,

26:03.510 --> 26:04.350
but as a human,

26:05.510 --> 26:07.240
you can't lack money.

26:11.590 --> 26:13.240
Bring more money with you

26:13.880 --> 26:15.110
when you go out.

26:17.350 --> 26:18.810
Don't mistreat yourself.

26:34.200 --> 26:35.350
Master also said

26:37.030 --> 26:38.760
that he has settled everything

26:39.000 --> 26:40.860
according to your instructions.

26:45.590 --> 26:47.720
This golden liquid doesn't just taste

26:47.750 --> 26:49.080
like the Yangyuan Pill,

26:49.510 --> 26:51.640
but its effects are also similar to it.

26:51.680 --> 26:52.350
However,

26:53.110 --> 26:55.640
it's much more potent
than the Yangyuan Pill.

26:55.880 --> 26:57.140
As long as you drink it,

26:57.270 --> 26:59.000
it instantly boosts your power

26:59.110 --> 27:00.370
and heals your wounds.

27:00.550 --> 27:01.110
It even

27:01.750 --> 27:03.070
prolongs life

27:03.350 --> 27:04.880
and elevates your realm.

27:05.790 --> 27:06.590
It's a pity

27:08.000 --> 27:09.110
we can't find out

27:10.390 --> 27:11.590
how it's made.

27:15.510 --> 27:16.640
What else did he say?

27:18.880 --> 27:19.790
He also said

27:20.680 --> 27:23.310
your path as a human isn't easy.

27:24.200 --> 27:26.270
Your power will weaken over time.

27:26.720 --> 27:27.680
When you're out,

27:28.590 --> 27:30.200
you must be extra careful.

27:32.790 --> 27:34.190
He really is getting old.

27:35.310 --> 27:36.370
He was about to die,

27:36.810 --> 27:38.010
yet still so nagging.

27:42.240 --> 27:43.160
He also said

27:44.030 --> 27:45.720
he should customarily

27:46.400 --> 27:48.350
kowtow to you before the end,

27:49.880 --> 27:51.200
but you were asleep.

27:52.070 --> 27:52.750
Let him

27:53.790 --> 27:54.830
skip it.

28:03.300 --> 28:05.350
♪ What do you think is ♪

28:05.400 --> 28:07.750
♪ The most clumsy farewell ♪

28:08.020 --> 28:11.200
♪ The endless slaughter and massacres ♪

28:12.000 --> 28:15.840
♪ Do not wait until that thin snow
on the eaves ♪

28:16.020 --> 28:19.720
♪ Turns a young man's hair white
before you regret it ♪

28:17.440 --> 28:18.110
Don't cry.

28:19.030 --> 28:20.400
You won't look pretty if you keep crying.

28:19.870 --> 28:21.220
♪ When you think ♪

28:21.250 --> 28:23.980
♪ The bloody strife
would come to an end? ♪

28:21.480 --> 28:23.140
Who looks pretty when crying?

28:23.400 --> 28:24.680
You're not allowed to dislike me.

28:24.000 --> 28:27.340
♪ End these everlasting battles ♪

28:27.480 --> 28:27.940
Let's go

28:27.960 --> 28:31.890
♪ Holding the morning glow in hand,
I paint the world ♪

28:32.020 --> 28:36.520
♪ Someone's got to clean up this mess ♪

28:48.900 --> 28:50.430
What's that sound outside?

28:52.160 --> 28:53.120
Master's coffin

28:53.400 --> 28:54.720
is in Longevity Hall.

28:55.110 --> 28:55.830
The sound

28:56.070 --> 28:57.680
must be coming from there.

29:06.520 --> 29:07.380
Senior Sister,

29:07.660 --> 29:08.520
are you hungry?

29:09.030 --> 29:10.760
I'll go cook something for you.

29:11.070 --> 29:11.930
I'm not hungry.

29:18.110 --> 29:20.570
Senior, are you going
to the Longevity Hall?

29:21.070 --> 29:21.590
Yes.

29:28.000 --> 29:29.060
Let's go together.

29:31.270 --> 29:33.470
Master practiced medicine all his life

29:33.960 --> 29:35.490
and saved countless lives.

29:35.830 --> 29:36.690
Over the years,

29:37.010 --> 29:37.790
he refined so many pills for

29:37.790 --> 29:39.110
the immortal sects.

29:40.070 --> 29:41.920
Now he has just passed away.

29:42.270 --> 29:44.270
How can you be so insolent?

29:44.790 --> 29:45.790
Insolent?

29:48.200 --> 29:50.720
To support Su Taiyi

29:50.790 --> 29:52.480
in refining the Immortality Pills,

29:52.480 --> 29:54.720
we gave everything we had.

29:55.860 --> 29:56.820
Without us,

29:57.070 --> 29:59.330
Chongling Valley wouldn't exist today.

29:59.640 --> 30:00.590
But now,

30:00.830 --> 30:02.230
he simply closes his eyes

30:02.480 --> 30:03.640
and dies so easily.

30:04.400 --> 30:05.750
The mess he left behind,

30:05.940 --> 30:07.400
who's going to clean it up?

30:07.750 --> 30:09.350
There must be an explanation

30:09.400 --> 30:10.530
for our sacrifices.

30:11.680 --> 30:12.750
Where are the Immortality Pills?

30:12.750 --> 30:13.680
He's already dead.

30:13.680 --> 30:14.880
What else do you want?

30:17.830 --> 30:18.510
Senior.

30:19.510 --> 30:20.910
Master just passed away.

30:21.350 --> 30:22.350
This is really not

30:22.350 --> 30:23.750
the time to discuss this.

30:24.160 --> 30:24.680
How about we

30:24.680 --> 30:26.350
arrange Master's funeral first

30:26.350 --> 30:27.940
before giving everyone an explanation?

30:27.940 --> 30:28.490
No.

30:29.350 --> 30:30.240
From now on,

30:30.680 --> 30:32.680
the Chongling Valley is closed.

30:33.450 --> 30:35.280
All the elixir recipes, herbs,

30:35.310 --> 30:35.880
books,

30:35.920 --> 30:37.440
and Su Taiyi's notes—

30:37.510 --> 30:39.240
even every

30:39.510 --> 30:41.030
discarded draft in the valley—

30:41.030 --> 30:42.290
we are taking them all.

30:43.350 --> 30:44.830
The third and fourth-generation disciples

30:44.830 --> 30:46.240
will be detained for interrogation.

30:46.240 --> 30:47.680
The second generation of disciples

30:47.680 --> 30:49.340
and Su Taiyi's body

30:49.640 --> 30:51.070
will return to Tianyuan Sect with me.

30:51.070 --> 30:51.800
How dare you!

30:52.070 --> 30:53.350
Why wouldn't we dare?

30:54.240 --> 30:56.510
We only respected Chongling Valley before

30:56.510 --> 30:57.700
because that old dog Su Taiyi

30:57.700 --> 30:59.080
was still alive.

30:59.640 --> 31:01.200
And we believed his lies

31:01.680 --> 31:02.640
and thought

31:02.790 --> 31:04.750
he could refine the immortality elixir.

31:04.750 --> 31:05.750
Do you weak

31:06.110 --> 31:07.510
and powerless mortals

31:07.750 --> 31:09.030
think you can defy us?

31:14.800 --> 31:17.890
♪ Sparks boil over,
and demons run rampant ♪

31:17.920 --> 31:19.920
♪ Heaven and earth
are destroyed together ♪

31:20.780 --> 31:22.510
♪ Deeply knowing that the common people ♪

31:22.540 --> 31:26.020
♪ Are an untouchable weakness ♪

31:27.270 --> 31:30.580
♪ Do not turn back
to the pain of the past ♪

31:31.020 --> 31:34.090
♪ Mindless killing must not be done ♪

31:33.070 --> 31:33.880
Who are you?

31:34.110 --> 31:38.910
♪ With a clear conscience, a grand spirit
overpowers the majesty of heaven ♪

31:34.270 --> 31:35.160
Who let you in?

31:39.160 --> 31:42.050
♪ I ask the Nine Heavens:
what is the purpose of this life? ♪

31:42.070 --> 31:45.070
♪ With my spine as my monument,
I shall never kneel ♪

31:45.730 --> 31:48.100
♪ By my will,
I shall bring back the sun and moon ♪

31:48.130 --> 31:51.340
♪ And restore clear radiance
to the mortal realm ♪

31:57.960 --> 31:58.640
Who are you?

31:59.720 --> 32:01.920
What is your relationship with Su Taiyi?

32:01.920 --> 32:03.380
Tell the people behind you

32:03.720 --> 32:05.200
that my name is Lu Qianqiao.

32:05.200 --> 32:06.460
I am Su Taiyi's master.

32:06.920 --> 32:07.750
You can come to me

32:07.750 --> 32:08.690
for anything.

32:09.260 --> 32:09.990
But if anyone

32:10.010 --> 32:11.880
dares to scheme against Chongling Valley,

32:11.880 --> 32:13.350
I will annihilate their entire sect,

32:13.350 --> 32:14.550
leaving no one alive.

32:21.550 --> 32:22.080
Get lost!

32:23.480 --> 32:25.950
♪ I ask the Nine Heavens:
what is the purpose of this life? ♪

32:24.760 --> 32:25.310
Our...

32:25.330 --> 32:26.790
Our paths will cross again.

32:26.310 --> 32:29.200
♪ With my spine as my monument,
I shall never kneel ♪

32:28.110 --> 32:29.170
Let's wait and see.

32:29.600 --> 32:32.640
♪ Rather than bowing my back
to apologize to the Heavens ♪

32:32.670 --> 32:35.720
♪ I would sooner rewrite
this fated calamity ♪

32:35.920 --> 32:38.430
♪ I demand the story
follow my own desire ♪

32:38.450 --> 32:41.560
♪ To serve as its final conclusion ♪

33:33.350 --> 33:34.000
Mr. Lu,

33:35.070 --> 33:36.000
are you alright?

33:36.830 --> 33:38.090
Have something to eat.

33:38.790 --> 33:39.310
No need.

33:49.750 --> 33:51.830
I ran into Divine Doctor Su
a few days ago.

33:51.830 --> 33:52.830
What he said

33:53.510 --> 33:55.040
had a profound impact on me.

33:56.200 --> 33:57.130
Hello, Miss Xin.

33:58.160 --> 33:59.180
Hello, Divine Doctor Su.

33:59.180 --> 34:00.120
Hello to you too.

34:01.720 --> 34:04.770
You look like you're in good spirits.

34:05.160 --> 34:07.290
A happy occasion lifts the spirit.

34:12.150 --> 34:12.760
Miss Xin,

34:13.510 --> 34:14.880
why do you look so pale?

34:15.230 --> 34:16.000
Are you sick?

34:18.280 --> 34:19.210
What's going on?

34:21.760 --> 34:22.670
Mr. Lu asked me

34:23.190 --> 34:25.300
if the Immortality Pills are good or bad,

34:25.300 --> 34:26.560
but I couldn't answer.

34:29.480 --> 34:31.800
So what do you really think?

34:32.429 --> 34:34.090
I think the Immortality Pills

34:34.340 --> 34:35.900
can make people immortal,

34:36.320 --> 34:37.920
which should be a good thing.

34:37.960 --> 34:39.070
But for their sake,

34:39.280 --> 34:40.880
many who should not have died

34:41.000 --> 34:42.600
ended up losing their lives.

34:43.510 --> 34:44.840
That's easy to explain.

34:45.360 --> 34:46.800
Wine can boost Yang energy,

34:46.800 --> 34:47.710
set the mood,

34:48.070 --> 34:49.389
and excite people.

34:49.840 --> 34:52.040
One drink can drown a thousand sorrows.

34:52.510 --> 34:54.310
It should be a good thing, right?

34:55.590 --> 34:56.880
But in years of famine,

34:56.960 --> 34:58.510
when there isn't even enough food to eat,

34:58.510 --> 35:00.440
if grain is still used to brew wine,

35:01.480 --> 35:03.510
can that wine

35:04.550 --> 35:05.760
be a good thing?

35:08.920 --> 35:09.630
Mr. Lu,

35:10.630 --> 35:11.510
I now think

35:12.150 --> 35:14.350
the Immortality Pills are a good thing.

35:15.510 --> 35:16.230
It's just

35:16.670 --> 35:17.760
like the wine

35:17.840 --> 35:19.170
brewed in a famine year.

35:19.590 --> 35:21.120
They are simply ill-timed.

35:21.920 --> 35:23.360
Whether it be the immortal sects

35:23.360 --> 35:24.560
or the secular world,

35:24.590 --> 35:26.550
including current laws, morality

35:26.840 --> 35:28.440
and the situation of common people

35:28.440 --> 35:30.710
is not enough to support their emergence.

35:30.710 --> 35:32.110
But one day in the future,

35:32.400 --> 35:33.840
I believe the Immortality Pills

35:33.840 --> 35:35.300
will surely appear again.

35:35.760 --> 35:36.800
And by then,

35:37.590 --> 35:38.880
not only the immortal sect,

35:38.880 --> 35:40.320
but ordinary people
will also be able to use them.

35:40.320 --> 35:41.920
They will benefit the world.

35:42.280 --> 35:44.440
So Divine Doctor Su's lifelong dedication

35:44.440 --> 35:45.440
has been worth it.

35:46.590 --> 35:47.440
Do you believe

35:48.190 --> 35:49.250
that day will come?

35:49.960 --> 35:50.400
Yes.

36:24.840 --> 36:26.570
When are you planning
to leave?

36:28.070 --> 36:29.210
Divine Doctor Su's funeral arrangements

36:29.210 --> 36:30.230
are almost done.

36:31.260 --> 36:32.140
We can

36:32.510 --> 36:33.440
leave tomorrow.

36:38.590 --> 36:39.190
Sheng.

36:40.230 --> 36:41.110
Do you remember

36:42.560 --> 36:44.330
the story our master

36:44.360 --> 36:45.280
told us before?

36:46.360 --> 36:46.960
Which one?

36:49.590 --> 36:50.440
He said

36:52.000 --> 36:53.260
there was a good person

36:54.030 --> 36:56.030
who did many good deeds in their life

36:56.710 --> 36:57.840
and had great merit.

36:58.840 --> 37:01.190
Later, they were wronged
and misunderstood.

37:01.190 --> 37:02.720
Many years after they died,

37:03.510 --> 37:04.770
people later found out

37:05.880 --> 37:07.610
that they didn't actually die,

37:08.960 --> 37:09.670
but

37:10.960 --> 37:12.820
ascended to heaven as an immortal

37:13.670 --> 37:14.800
to enjoy blessings.

37:15.760 --> 37:17.290
I don't want to go to heaven,

37:18.110 --> 37:19.770
nor do I want to be an immortal.

37:25.550 --> 37:27.480
I just want to stay in Xin Xie Manor.

37:47.920 --> 37:48.630
Master,

37:49.440 --> 37:50.840
have a safe journey.

37:51.880 --> 37:52.740
Drink less wine

37:53.320 --> 37:54.670
down there.

37:55.300 --> 37:57.530
[The Tomb of the Divine Doctor Su Taiyi]

37:55.490 --> 37:56.550
In a few years,

37:57.190 --> 37:58.280
I will go down

37:58.670 --> 37:59.710
to serve you.

38:00.230 --> 38:00.920
Master.

38:01.640 --> 38:02.590
The zither player in the valley

38:02.590 --> 38:03.510
passed away

38:04.400 --> 38:05.400
from a sudden illness

38:05.400 --> 38:06.150
last night.

38:06.840 --> 38:09.710
You loved listening
to her play while you were alive.

38:09.710 --> 38:10.970
So, you won't be lonely

38:11.280 --> 38:12.680
on the journey together.

38:26.760 --> 38:27.960
Have you said enough?

38:28.510 --> 38:29.770
If you're still angry,

38:29.800 --> 38:31.170
then keep hitting me

38:31.230 --> 38:32.510
until you calm down.

38:32.960 --> 38:33.710
Couldn't you

38:34.150 --> 38:36.590
pretend you didn't know about this?

38:37.320 --> 38:38.320
In a few days,

38:38.510 --> 38:40.240
the medicine will take effect,

38:40.590 --> 38:42.110
and you can renew bones.

38:42.550 --> 38:43.070
By then,

38:43.230 --> 38:45.490
you'll be one step closer to being human.

38:45.770 --> 38:47.230
Couldn't you just stay focused on

38:47.230 --> 38:48.050
doing your own thing

38:48.050 --> 38:49.650
and ignore everything else?

38:59.880 --> 39:00.210
Look,

39:00.550 --> 39:02.010
there are river lanterns.

39:05.030 --> 39:06.960
The people knew Master passed away

39:07.190 --> 39:09.050
and wanted to pay their respects.

39:09.150 --> 39:10.630
I sent people stop them.

39:11.960 --> 39:12.890
They know

39:12.920 --> 39:14.650
Master's grave is by the river.

39:14.960 --> 39:16.160
Some people have been

39:16.760 --> 39:18.890
releasing lanterns since last night.

39:27.400 --> 39:28.600
You're heading back?

39:30.800 --> 39:32.460
We've been out for a long time.

39:32.510 --> 39:33.910
Things here are settled.

39:34.070 --> 39:35.200
It's time to go back.

39:37.190 --> 39:38.050
What about you?

39:38.280 --> 39:38.880
Mr. Lu,

39:39.550 --> 39:40.680
what are your plans?

39:42.150 --> 39:43.410
I'll go to North Xiang.

39:45.360 --> 39:45.960
Mr. Lu,

39:46.760 --> 39:48.840
will we meet again?

39:50.090 --> 39:50.690
Of course.

39:52.920 --> 39:53.850
Our Xin Xie Manor

39:53.880 --> 39:55.510
is at the foot of Tianyuan Mountain,

39:55.510 --> 39:56.570
near Yanzhou City,

39:56.760 --> 39:58.030
and right next to Lake Boyang.

39:58.030 --> 39:59.280
My master is well-known.

39:59.280 --> 40:00.150
Just ask around nearby.

40:00.150 --> 40:01.280
Everyone knows him.

40:03.920 --> 40:04.920
Do you know

40:04.920 --> 40:06.520
where Tianyuan Mountain is?

40:07.150 --> 40:07.800
Yes.

40:09.710 --> 40:11.510
If you come back from North Xiang

40:11.630 --> 40:12.690
and have free time,

40:13.000 --> 40:14.130
you can come find me.

40:14.440 --> 40:16.110
There are countless mountains
where I'm from.

40:16.110 --> 40:16.870
The peaks rise one after another,

40:16.710 --> 40:21.300
♪ Spending a lifetime,
I ask myself what I first sought ♪

40:17.110 --> 40:18.320
and the scenery is fantastic.

40:18.320 --> 40:19.000
It's also unlike

40:19.000 --> 40:20.480
Tianyuan Mountain, which is so dry.

40:20.480 --> 40:21.580
In our Xin Xie Manor,

40:21.580 --> 40:22.340
it's not severely cold in winter

40:22.340 --> 40:27.300
♪ What is it my heart truly desires? ♪

40:22.480 --> 40:23.440
or extremely hot in summer.

40:23.440 --> 40:24.510
There is also a lot of good food.

40:24.510 --> 40:25.440
My favorite is

40:25.440 --> 40:27.290
the Rice Noodles with Lamb
from Yanzhou City.

40:27.290 --> 40:28.440
If you ever come,

40:27.710 --> 40:30.530
♪ Step by step up the immortal stairway ♪

40:28.670 --> 40:30.670
I will definitely take you to try it.

40:30.800 --> 40:31.150
Okay.

40:31.070 --> 40:33.600
♪ Paved with countless lost souls ♪

40:32.630 --> 40:34.230
Then it's settled.

40:34.240 --> 40:39.350
♪ Who would dare destroy the ladder
to immortality and end the path? ♪

40:36.070 --> 40:36.800
For sure.

40:38.400 --> 40:39.260
Senior Sister,

40:39.590 --> 40:40.340
get on the boat.

40:40.340 --> 40:45.510
♪ The sun blazes over the earth ♪

40:43.100 --> 40:44.500
Do you want to come along?

40:46.400 --> 40:48.070
I still need to wait for someone.

40:46.540 --> 40:51.880
♪ Yet it cannot warm
every cold home below ♪

40:50.740 --> 40:51.910
North Xiang is a long way off.

40:51.910 --> 40:54.870
♪ I've heard cries that rend the heavens ♪

40:52.440 --> 40:52.900
Senior,

40:53.590 --> 40:54.720
take care on the way.

40:55.470 --> 40:57.830
♪ I hear the shame of parting ♪

40:55.550 --> 40:56.280
Take care.

40:58.060 --> 41:00.450
♪ This immortal path admired by all ♪

41:00.670 --> 41:03.380
♪ Can exist, or not exist ♪

41:03.550 --> 41:06.200
♪ Once again I see
the world's cold indifference ♪

41:06.230 --> 41:09.330
♪ Bending what I've cherished
all my life ♪

41:09.560 --> 41:15.190
♪ Illusions and vanity blind the eyes,
how could one still care ♪

41:15.630 --> 41:18.150
♪ Having seen the widespread devastation ♪

41:18.180 --> 41:21.240
♪ How could I look on and ignore it? ♪

41:22.020 --> 41:24.160
♪ I do not fear returning to dust ♪

41:24.180 --> 41:27.340
♪ I walk this path alone ♪

41:27.690 --> 41:30.500
♪ So that all may share in ♪

41:30.530 --> 41:33.460
♪ The road to immortality ♪

41:33.490 --> 41:40.110
♪ I fear not defying
immortal laws and sacred precepts ♪

41:43.880 --> 41:44.740
Still looking?

41:45.630 --> 41:46.760
She's already gone.

41:48.030 --> 41:49.230
When did you get back?

41:50.030 --> 41:51.800
Have you burned incense for Su?

41:53.190 --> 41:53.800
I have.

41:54.510 --> 41:56.510
I even poured two pots

41:56.630 --> 41:58.760
of liquor I brought back
from Fangwai Mountain on his grave.

41:58.760 --> 42:00.190
If he knows in the underworld,

42:00.190 --> 42:01.550
he must be very happy.

42:03.320 --> 42:04.360
One piece of good news

42:04.360 --> 42:05.510
and one piece of bad news.

42:05.510 --> 42:07.240
Which do you want to hear first?

42:08.110 --> 42:08.770
The bad one.

42:10.440 --> 42:11.920
I went to Fangwai Mountain,

42:11.920 --> 42:13.090
but I couldn't find

42:13.190 --> 42:15.450
the magical artifact for blood renewal.

42:15.690 --> 42:16.690
And the good news?

42:19.400 --> 42:20.460
I came back safely.

42:22.320 --> 42:23.720
That really is good news.

42:25.400 --> 42:26.530
What's the plan now?

42:26.760 --> 42:27.710
Do you want to stay in Chongling Valley

42:27.710 --> 42:28.770
to rest for a while,

42:28.920 --> 42:30.050
or continue looking

42:30.360 --> 42:31.690
for a way to renew blood?

42:32.210 --> 42:33.130
I've already found it.
